The Report Issue dialog skill assists your end users in getting their issues resolved by agents. It can replace or augment an existing Web2Case form.

The first rule recognizes if a case was created through the pre-chat form. If so, the bot displays a custom message and allows the user to go back to the Main Menu to report another case, if needed.

Create Case

The action dialog step creates a case, built similarly to the Create Lead action. However, this flow also outputs the case number, so users can reference it later.
